id='GLOBAL_BD_TOP'></div><div class="row"><div class="col-md-8"><article class="news-item single hentry"><div class="io-word-count" style="display: none;">538</div><h2 class="entry-title"><a href="https://www.softzone.es/2017/02/07/principales-diferencias-firmware-drivers-software/">Principales diferencias entre el firmware, drivers y software</a></h2><div class="news-author clearfix"><div class="vcard pull-left"> Escrito por <span class="author fn">David Onieva</span></div> <time class="pull-right published updated" datetime="2017-02-07 17:00:51"><span>Febrero 7, 2017<span class="hidden-xs"> a las 17:00</span></span></time></div><div class="news-meta"><div class="news-meta-category category-curiosidades text-lowercase pull-left"><i class="fa "></i>Curiosidades</div><div class="news-meta-social pull-left"> <a href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?s=100&p[url]=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.softzone.es%2F2017%2F02%2F07%2Fprincipales-diferencias-firmware-drivers-software%2F&p[title]=Principales+diferencias+entre+el+firmware%2C+drivers+y+software" onclick="javascript:window.open(this.href, '', 'menubar=no,toolbar=no,resizable=yes,scrollbars=yes,height=600,width=600');return false;"><i class="fa fa-facebook"></i></a> <a href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.softzone.es%2F2017%2F02%2F07%2Fprincipales-diferencias-firmware-drivers-software%2F&text=Principales+diferencias+entre+el+firmware%2C+drivers+y+software&via=softzone"><i class="fa fa-twitter"></i></a> <a href="https://plus.google.com/share?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.softzone.es%2F2017%2F02%2F07%2Fprincipales-diferencias-firmware-drivers-software%2F&text=Principales+diferencias+entre+el+firmware%2C+drivers+y+software" onclick="javascript:window.open(this.href, '', 'menubar=no,toolbar=no,resizable=yes,scrollbars=yes,height=600,width=600');return false;"><i class="fa fa-google-plus"></i></a></div><div class="news-meta-comments pull-right"><a href="#comments"><span class="badge"><span class="dsq-postid" data-dsqidentifier="140304 https://www.softzone.es/?p=140304">0</span></span></a> <i class="fa fa-comments-o"></i></div></div><div class="featured-image"> <img
data-bttrlazyloading-lg-src="https://www.softzone.es/app/uploads/2017/02/software.jpg?x=634&y=309"
data-bttrlazyloading-lg-width="634"
